Bugs
    Extra new line on top of Commands & Push Messages
    do not send $G/$# for:
        $SLP, maybe others
    Scrolling
        Only scroll to end if view position is already at the end
            if not, change color to indicate there's new text
    Connecting to Grbl via TCP sometimes hangs
    When $H is active, if ^C it locks on exit
        ControlPrimitive.RunSendCommandWorker calls app.QueueUpdate indirectly
        on Control.Run, on the defer, the context is cancelled, and at this point, the app is stopped.
        app.QueueUpdate does not handle this case: it stalls, as there's no app run loop to process it
        proper fix would require app.QueueUpdate to return when the app is stopped.
        workaround is to run QueueUpdate in a separate goroutine (which may cause other concurrency issues
